Program: The Forum
Title: Risor Festival: Outcasts
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0227gbb
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 14 Jul 2014
From the Risor Festival in Norway, presenter Bridget Kendall hears from four distinguished Scandinavians and an attentive festival audience on the topic of the uninvited. With film director Margreth Olin, bioethicist Bjorn Hofmann, Icelandic writer Sjón and violinist Henning Kraggerud. (Photo: Bridget Kendall, Margreth Olin, Bjorn Hofmann, Sjón and Henning Kraggerud in front of an invited audience. Credit: Liv Øvland/Risør Chamber Music Festival) Show less